        {
            "title": "據報高盛月內第2次下調中國股指目標",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">關稅戰爆發，為環球股市投下顯著不明朗因素。美資大行高盛據報也在月內第2次下調對中國股指的目標。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"高盛 Goldman Sachs (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240416_FI_source-ap_Goldman_Sachs.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"高盛 Goldman Sachs (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240416_FI_source-ap_Goldman_Sachs.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">高盛 Goldman Sachs (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》引述高盛報告，表示已將MSCI中國指數和滬深300指數的12個月目標價，分別下調至75點和4300點，以反映較壞的風險情景，亦即全球經濟普遍衰退，中國經濟增長和政策亦令人失望。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報告指出，若有大幅降低關稅的潛在貿易協議，仍有望令中國股市估值提升最多35%；高盛現仍看好A股多於H股，在板塊當中將銀行與房地產上調至至超配。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14852493-%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e9%ab%98%e7%9b%9b%e6%9c%88%e5%85%a7%e7%ac%ac2%e6%ac%a1%e4%b8%8b%e8%aa%bf%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e8%82%a1%e6%8c%87%e7%9b%ae%e6%a8%99",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230828_FI_source-web_SSE.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-14 10:20:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
